FT  12 SEP 92 / Finance &amp; the Family: Invesco to pay compensation
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Invesco MIM, the fund management group, said this week it would be paying
compensation to Drayton Consolidated Investment Trust, which it manages, for
