trust. None of the disappearing trusts has performed well; the Gold Trust,
in a process of reverse alchemy, has turned Pounds 100 into a leaden Pounds
29.30 over the past five years. Unitholders should not necessarily expect an
improvement; the International Growth trust is 36th out of 38 trusts in its
sector over 10 years.
